  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747430/extras/db312a260f80bb67798a50c17640b06e.poster.avif?t=1679680721\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747430/extras/db312a260f80bb67798a50c17640b06e.webm?t=1679680721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747430/extras/db312a260f80bb67798a50c17640b06e.mp4?t=1679680721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Bomberpet is a multiplayer game with an overhead view and simple controls. In fact, in addition to movement, the player has different abilities due to the power-ups he can collect during the game. Each bomb explodes in four directions, the explosion can destroy enemies or destroy walls. Various bonuses can be found in the walls. The goal of each level is to destroy all enemies. At the end of each game you get rewards.<br><br><strong>In the game you can.</strong><br>- Change the appearance of the character.<br>- Change the type of bombs.<br>- Fight with other players.<br>- Put bombs, blow up other players. <br>- Collect active items, they improve the player's abilities.<br>- Break down walls, making your way to other players.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747430/extras/db312a260f80bb67798a50c17640b06e.poster.avif?t=1679680721\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747430/extras/db312a260f80bb67798a50c17640b06e.webm?t=1679680721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747430/extras/db312a260f80bb67798a50c17640b06e.mp4?t=1679680721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Bomberpet is a multiplayer game with an overhead view and simple controls. In fact, in addition to movement, the player has different abilities due to the power-ups he can collect during the game. Each bomb explodes in four directions, the explosion can destroy enemies or destroy walls. Various bonuses can be found in the walls. The goal of each level is to destroy all enemies. At the end of each game you get rewards.<br><br><strong>In the game you can.</strong><br>- Change the appearance of the character.<br>- Change the type of bombs.<br>- Fight with other players.<br>- Put bombs, blow up other players. <br>- Collect active items, they improve the player's abilities.<br>- Break down walls, making your way to other players.",
